nl.unimaas.msb.psbap.utils

Class AAprops

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.unimaas.msb.psbap.utils.AAprops

  • public class AAprops
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility class to use 48 amino acid properties in creating features for AA residues and their surrounding It can calculate the AA properties for all residues surrounding a specific residue with 8A radius and return the results as a list of double values
    Author:
    Ammar Ammar
